    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hornpipes of southern Scotland, with a tube of wood or bone, elongated wood mouthpiece, a bell of natural animal horn, and single reed.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
